---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ELS Catalyst – SEO, PR och hemsidor för lokala företag</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Vi hjälper lokala och mindre företag att synas online – med SEO, PR och professionella hemsidor som faktiskt ger resultat." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --dark: #0b1120;
      --dark2: #111827;
      --accent: #6366f1;
      --accent-light: #818cf8;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --radius: 12px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(11, 17, 32, 0.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      height: 64px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    nav a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover { color: white; }

    .btn-nav {
      background: var(--accent) !important;
      color: white !important;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem !important;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600 !important;
    }

    .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--accent-light) !important; }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b1120 0%, #1a1040 100%);
      padding: 7rem 1.5rem 6rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99,102,241,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.3);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-light);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-badge::before {
      content: '';
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.4; }
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #818cf8, #c084fc);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(99,102,241,0.35);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); }

    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 4rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat { text-align: center; }

    .stat-num {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }

    .section-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .section-desc {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 560px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* SERVICES */
    #tjanster { background: var(--bg); }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.1);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .service-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .service-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .service-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    .service-list li {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .service-list li::before {
      content: '';
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* USPs */
    .usps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .usp { text-align: center; }

    .usp-icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99,102,241,0.15), rgba(192,132,252,0.1));
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .usp h4 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .usp p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* CASES */
    #case { background: var(--dark); }
    #case .section-title { color: white; }
    #case .section-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
    #case .section-label { color: var(--accent-light); }

    .cases-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .case-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .case-card:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.4);
    }

    .case-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.15);
      color: var(--accent-light);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .case-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .case-card p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Browser mockup */
    .browser-mockup {
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .browser-bar {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .browser-dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    .browser-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .browser-dot:nth-child(1) { background: #ff5f56; }
    .browser-dot:nth-child(2) { background: #ffbd2e; }
    .browser-dot:nth-child(3) { background: #27c93f; }

    .browser-url {
      flex: 1;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      font-family: monospace;
    }

    .browser-screenshot {
      width: 100%;
      height: 160px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: top;
      display: block;
    }

    .case-results {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      padding-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .case-result { flex: 1; }

    .case-result-num {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent-light);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .case-result-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    /* CONTACT */
    #kontakt { background: var(--bg); }

    .contact-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .contact-info {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-item-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .contact-item-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .contact-item-value {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .contact-item-value a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-item-value a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    .contact-form {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2.25rem;
    }

    .contact-form h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .contact-form > p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .form-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group select,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.875rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      outline: none;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group select:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99,102,241,0.1);
    }

    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 110px; }

    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.875rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .btn-submit:hover {
      background: var(--accent-light);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      background: var(--dark2);
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { display: none; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cases-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .usps-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .contact-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero { padding: 5rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 2rem; }
      .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="header-inner">
      <a href="#" class="logo">
        <div class="logo-mark">EC</div>
        <span class="logo-text">ELS Catalyst</span>
      </a>
      <nav>
        <a href="#tjanster">Tjänster</a>
        <a href="#varfor">Varför oss</a>
        <a href="#case">Case</a>
        <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-nav">Prata med oss</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">För lokala och mindre företag</div>
    <h1>Syns du inte online<br><span>finns du knappt</span></h1>
    <p>Vi hjälper lokala och mindre företag att ranka högre på Google, nå rätt kunder och bygga en digital närvaro som faktiskt konverterar.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-primary">Boka kostnadsfri genomgång</a>
      <a href="#case" class="btn-secondary">Se våra resultat</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">+180%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Snittökning organisk trafik</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">20+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Nöjda kunder</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">3 veckor</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Från start till live</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section id="tjanster">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Vad vi gör</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Allt du behöver för att synas och växa</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Vi arbetar med tre kärnområden som driver verkliga resultat för lokala och mindre företag.</p>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">&#128269;</div>
          <h3>SEO</h3>
          <p>Vi optimerar din sajt så att dina kunder hittar dig — inte konkurrenterna — när de söker på Google.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Lokal sökmotoroptimering</li>
            <li>Teknisk SEO och sidhastighet</li>
            <li>Innehållsstrategi och sökordsanalys</li>
            <li>Google Business Profile</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">&#128240;</div>
          <h3>PR &amp; synlighet</h3>
          <p>Vi sätter din berättelse i rätt sammanhang — med lokal media, digitala publikationer och social närvaro.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Pressreleaser och mediakontakter</li>
            <li>Länkbyggnad för stärkt trovärdighet</li>
            <li>Varumärkespositionering</li>
            <li>Expertuttalanden och thought leadership</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">&#128187;</div>
          <h3>Hemsida</h3>
          <p>Professionella, snabba hemsidor byggda för att konvertera besökare till kunder — inte bara imponera.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Design och utveckling</li>
            <li>SEO-optimerad från dag ett</li>
            <li>Mobil-first och snabb laddning</li>
            <li>Löpande underhåll och uppdateringar</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- USPs -->
  <section id="varfor">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Varför ELS Catalyst</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Vi jobbar som en del av ditt team</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Inga långa byrårelationer, inga onödiga mellanhänder. Du pratar direkt med personen som gör jobbet.</p>

      <div class="usps-grid">
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-icon">&#127919;</div>
          <h4>Fokus på resultat</h4>
          <p>Vi mäter allt och rapporterar i siffror — klick, trafik, leads. Inte fina presentationer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-icon">&#129309;</div>
          <h4>Personlig kontakt</h4>
          <p>Du har alltid direkt access till oss. Ingen ticketsupport, inga svarsmallar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-icon">&#9889;</div>
          <h4>Snabb leverans</h4>
          <p>Från brief till lansering på 2–3 veckor. Vi respekterar din tid och ditt tempo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-icon">&#128200;</div>
          <h4>Lokal expertis</h4>
          <p>Vi förstår den svenska marknaden och hur lokala kunder söker och fattar beslut.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CASES -->
  <section id="case">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Resultat vi skapat</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Case</h2>
